<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div xml:id="Aink128">
      <lg type="edition">
<l>kaṇṭiku mallamō koṇkaniṉ kēḷē</l>
<l>yuṟāa vaṟu mulai maṭāa</l>
<l>vuṇṇāp pāvaiyai yūṭṭu vōḷē.</l>
</lg>
<lg type="translation" xml:lang="en">
<l>We have seen your friend, haven't we, oh man from the maritime tract?</l>
<l>She who feeds a doll that does not take drink [and] that does not eat,</l>
<l>With her scarce, poor breasts.</l>
</lg>
    </div>
